articles.author: Matthew Loh
articles.title: Lost dog treks 150 miles on frozen Alaskan sea and returns home - Insider
articles.description: Nanuq the Australian Shepherd is only a year old, but survived a nearly month-long trek through polar bear territory on the frozen Bering Strait.
articles.content:
A dog that went missing in Alaska last month has arrived home safely after making a 150-mile trek on the frozen Bering Sea.
